    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Using Loops\r\nJoel made a beat that he loves, but he doesn't know how to use loops yet.\r\n\r\nHis code works, but it's long and hard to follow because it repeats the same beats over and over.\r\n\r\n**Your task:** Use **abstraction** to simplify Joel's remix. Replace the repeated beats with loop blocks that hide the repetition behind a simple structure. Your remix should sound the same, just written in a smarter way!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/00cb2ed9d1462558388b475480c5b86c-image-1741897772945.29.26 PM.png)",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
